CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 5, 1957, page A12-13, reads: "The Domestic Touch is given by Evelyn Cunningham, left, and Gladys Johnson, who will make the handsome trailer (completely equipped with bedrooms, bath and kitchen) their traveling home for the next two and a half months. Mrs. Cunningham and Mrs. Johnson, plus Jimmy Johnson and Jake Gaither, were at Wilberforce, Ohio, where they spoke at Wilberforce University and Central State College Thursday and Friday Oct. 3 and 4. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Evelyn Cunningham, left, and Gladys Johnson wearing a dress with design around collar and an apron with tassels, leaning over drawer holding wood spoon in kitchen with stove, lace curtains over window, iron on counter, and light colored cabinets
